✴ Portrait of Gatherer

Gatherer swims around the space, collecting lost sparkles of hopes and dreams. It processes them and combines them into the new one. All is not lost. Any small light is important.

✴[MAD GOD]✴ is an original dark fantasy series consisting of blood and beautiful creatures portraying their life, their pride, and their attitude.
